NAM TAEWOO

5
00:01:44,271 --> 00:01:45,271
Hello?

6
00:01:45,272 --> 00:01:46,605
Hey...

7
00:01:46,606 --> 00:01:48,357
<i>Is this Juhyeong?</i>

8
00:01:48,358 --> 00:01:49,567
Hey, it's been a while.

9
00:01:49,568 --> 00:01:51,903
<i>Hey, how are you doing?</i>

10
00:01:52,821 --> 00:01:54,489
Yeah, I'm good.

11
00:01:56,366 --> 00:01:57,366
What's up?

12
00:01:57,367 --> 00:02:00,829
<i>Geez, this is kind of awkward
to talk about.</i>

13
00:02:01,663 --> 00:02:04,623
<i>I briefly went out
with this client of mine,</i>

14
00:02:04,624 --> 00:02:07,502
<i>but it turns out she's a married woman.</i>

15
00:02:09,546 --> 00:02:10,546
Okay. So?

16
00:02:10,547 --> 00:02:12,340
Well, anyway,

17
00:02:12,341 --> 00:02:16,553
her husband told everyone at work
I'm the guy she cheated with.

18
00:02:17,137 --> 00:02:20,848
Is there any way
to stop this rumor from spreading?

19
00:02:20,849 --> 00:02:22,767
Well, you can't physically stop him.

20
00:02:22,768 --> 00:02:25,102
You can't chase him around
and keep him quiet.

21
00:02:25,103 --> 00:02:27,647
Isn't there anything I can do legally?

22
00:02:27,648 --> 00:02:29,940
You won't be able to stop him directly.

23
00:02:29,941 --> 00:02:32,526
- What about an affair lawsuit?
<i>- It hasn't come up.</i>

24
00:02:32,527 --> 00:02:34,445
<i>If I didn't know she was married,</i>

25
00:02:34,446 --> 00:02:36,365
<i>I don't need to worry, right?</i>

26
00:02:37,949 --> 00:02:38,950
You didn't know?

27
00:02:39,743 --> 00:02:42,036
I honestly didn't know.

28
00:02:42,037 --> 00:02:46,040
I have all the texts
that show she lied about being single.

29
00:02:46,041 --> 00:02:47,959
I see. That won't be a problem then.

30
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:51,462
Are you suing for defamation?
I'll refer you to another lawyer.

31
00:02:51,463 --> 00:02:53,798
That depends
on where the water is leaking from.

32
00:02:53,799 --> 00:02:57,386
Depending on whether it's leaking
from upstairs or a shared pipe,

33
00:02:58,220 --> 00:03:00,013
it changes who's responsible.

34
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:04,726
Right, you won't know
until you open it up.

35
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,856
I don't know.

36
00:03:10,857 --> 00:03:13,610
I'm a lawyer, not a plumber.

37
00:03:14,361 --> 00:03:16,613
Okay, bye.

38
00:03:22,577 --> 00:03:23,662
Seriously...

39
00:03:26,248 --> 00:03:27,249
Hi.

40
00:03:30,210 --> 00:03:32,462
Is there any reason
to sue the security guard?

41
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:41,429
So everyone is okay
with that law student intern program

42
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:43,472
I mentioned last time, right?

43
00:03:43,473 --> 00:03:45,141
I can't afford to do that.

44
00:03:45,142 --> 00:03:47,184
A lot of small costs
add up here and there.

45
00:03:47,185 --> 00:03:49,729
- How will you handle that?
- You won't have to worry.

46
00:03:50,313 --> 00:03:52,857
It won't be any trouble to you.
I'll take care of it.

47
00:03:52,858 --> 00:03:54,316
Okay, then. If you say so.

48
00:03:54,317 --> 00:03:56,862
I don't have much of a reason to say no.

49
00:03:57,696 --> 00:04:00,239
But honestly, I'm not sure
if it's necessary.

50
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,991
Well, I've never done it before.

51
00:04:01,992 --> 00:04:04,619
