67
00:05:01,843 --> 00:05:03,053
Thank you so much.

68
00:05:03,637 --> 00:05:06,514
I'll do my best to make it work.

69
00:05:06,515 --> 00:05:07,682
Can I order a dessert?

70
00:05:09,893 --> 00:05:10,936
Of course.

71
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:12,770
Do you like meringues?

72
00:05:12,771 --> 00:05:14,147
- Seriously...
- What?

73
00:05:16,316 --> 00:05:18,151
Yes, thank you.

